article.description: — Darius McGhee had 19 points and six rebounds as Liberty got past Maryland Eastern Shore 73-61 on Saturday.
article.headline: McGhee scores 19 to lift Liberty over UMES 73-61
article.linkText: McGhee scores 19 to lift Liberty over UMES 73-61
article.story: LYNCHBURG, Va. -- — Darius McGhee had 19 points and six rebounds as Liberty got past Maryland Eastern Shore 73-61 on Saturday. Keegan McDowell had 16 points for Liberty (3-3). Shiloh Robinson added 13 points and seven rebounds. Dom London had 16 points for the Hawks (2-4). Donchevell Nugent added 10 points. Zion Styles had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
